    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，Rejected要流转到FraudDetection做风险分析。Confirmed之后更复杂，用户到场check-in就进入InProgress，如果超时没到场就是NoShow，也可以主动取消。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Rejected",
        "FinTech_FraudDetection",
        "Confirmed",
        "InProgress",
        "NoShow",
        "Cancelled",
        "check"
