      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "InProgress之后也有两个出口：正常结束到Completed，或者紧急情况取消。Completed要回到PaymentGateway做结算，Cancelled和NoShow都走LedgerService记账。",
      "elements_involved": [
